      "rationale": "Eleven constructs were fabricated from production-representative 7.5 mm non-cannulated Ti-6Al-4V pedicle screws and UHMWPE vertebral body blocks per ASTM F1717. Testing was split across two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH and DePuy Synthes) to assess inter-laboratory variability. Certificates of conformance and dimensional inspection records are archived in the design history file. Gradation 2 (production-representative samples, multi-lab) achieved and required."
